g.text: From the main menu, navigate to DOWNLOAD, then
Enter the password, then select Automatic Model Selection.
The password can be found on TriumphOnline.
Click Start. Is the model detected correctly?
Is the current calibration up to date? Refer to the calibration
Select the correct calibration for your region. Click Next.
Check the selected calibration is correct for your model and
Allow the download to complete. This should take
Position a paired key in range.
For US markets only, turn the ignition master switch ON.
Press the Power ON/OFF button to turn the motorcycle power On.
Ensure the engine Start/Stop switch is in the STOP (OFF) position.
Click Finish when the download has completed. Check all
ECMs for stored DTCs and erase as neccesary.
